Customers are facing problems to clone through SSH due to a bug on Apache Mina.

* https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SSHD-886

The workaround is to set an option in my ~/.ssh/config file:

{code}
#!python

AllowPKCS12keystoreAutoOpen no
{code}
